name: Green Man Mask
description: Found in an ancient woodland in Devon, UK. On a woodland walk a family came across this mask whilst playing around an old Yew tree, the dog was the first to spot it, barking. After inspecting the spot they caught a glimpse of a face within some foliage and moss in a crevice within the trunk. As they picked the mask up they realised they had come across a mask of the fabled Green Man. This was no ordinary mask, as with all the other legendary masks, this one too had a life of it's own. It is believed that the family were too spooked by it's otherworldly life that they left it where they found it.
